### ============================================================
### FAQS API REQUESTS
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000/v1
### ============================================================

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================================
### PUBLIC ROUTES (No Authentication Required)
### ============================================================

### Get all active FAQs
GET {{baseUrl}}/faqs
Content-Type: application/json

### Expected Response:
# {
#     "success": true,
#     "message": "FAQs fetched successfully",
#     "data": {
#         "faqs": [
#             {
#                 "id": 1,
#                 "question": "How can I report an issue in my community?",
#                 "answer": "You can report issues through our mobile app or by contacting your local field agent...",
#                 "category": "general",
#                 "display_order": 0
#             }
#         ]
#     }
# }

###

### Get FAQ categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/faqs/categories
Content-Type: application/json

### Expected Response:
# {
#     "success": true,
#     "message": "Categories fetched successfully",
#     "data": {
#         "categories": ["general", "projects", "services", "contact"]
#     }
# }

###

### ============================================================
### ADMIN ROUTES (Requires web_admin role)
### ============================================================

### Get all FAQs (including inactive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/faqs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get single FAQ
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/faqs/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Create new FAQ
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/faqs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "question": "What projects is the constituency currently undertaking?",
    "answer": "We are currently undertaking several development projects including road construction, school renovation, and water supply installation. Visit our Projects page for detailed information.",
    "category": "projects",
    "status": "active"
}

###

### Update FAQ
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/faqs/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "question": "Updated question?",
    "answer": "Updated answer with more details...",
    "status": "active"
}

###

### Reorder FAQs
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/faqs/reorder
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "order": [3, 1, 2, 4]
}

###

### Delete FAQ
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/faqs/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###
